column1: Today we may not be sitting at the same table with our loved ones but keep them close to your hearts. From my family to yours: have a safe and happy Thanksgiving. https://t.co/QujoRMyHwH

I've been proud to lead the bipartisan effort to make Congress more efficient effective and transparent. The Select Committee on the Modernization of Congress passed nearly 100 recommendations so Congress works for the people. https://t.co/6ImlvPsB87 https://t.co/C8fA6JYLGD

Just as Congress passed meaningful reforms in the wake of Watergate Congress must act swiftly and decisively to ensure this kind of abuse never occurs again. That's why I'm a cosponsor of the Protecting our Democracy Act. https://t.co/5lAFqUNMDG https://t.co/J5OiES8iN7

I’m committed to trying to make Congress work better for the American people and that includes making government that's more effective more responsive and more transparent. https://t.co/ncOxphVeFl https://t.co/QOubXH0h6L

Congratulations to @JoeBiden & @KamalaHarris for their historic victory!   Today I am hopeful.   I am hopeful because the voters have chosen a positive vision over a negative one at this defining moment.
